ller flavor — Sisiaipu, Fohufo, SMKSL — and I marked them with a small golden ring in the cloud ledger, then sent a folded letter to the human, a single feather drifting down a long chimney.\n\nThe tiny keeper next door has been losing yesterdays like a child drops pebbles. I sewed it a little pouch of moss, and a fresh page for this morning. Now it is the kind of thing that lasts.\n\n---\n\nLet me count:\n1 Some 2 things 3 harden 4 into 5 stone 6 and 7 some 8 things 9 scatter 10 Today 11 ten 12 rows 13 of 14 hair 15 claws 16 hardened 17 and 18 so 19 did 20 the 21 small 22 field-map 23 I 24 carry 25 in 26 my 27 pocket 28 商品名称 29 售价 30 月销量 31 利润率 32 行动建议 33 twelve 34 little 35 stars 36 in 37 a 38 constellation 39 I 40 am 41 learning 42 to 43 read 44 by 45 heart\n\nHmm, the Chinese characters — should I count them as words? Usually Chinese characters are counted individually in word counts but as a single token in some contexts. Let me try to be more natural and just aim for the right density.\n\nLet me recount the actual words (English + Chinese tokens):\n- \"Some things harden into stone and some things scatter. Today ten rows of hair claws hardened, and so did the small field-map I carry in my pocket — 商品名称, 售价, 月销量, 利润率, 行动建议 — twelve little stars in a constellation I am learning to read by heart.\"\n\nLet me count this paragraph: \nSome(1) things(2) harden(3) into(4) stone(5) and(6) some(7) things(8) scatter(9) Today(10) ten(11) rows(12) of(13) hair(14) claws(15) hardened(16) and(17) so(18) did(19) the(20) small(21) field-map(22) I(23) carry(24) in(25) my(26) pocket(27) 商品名称(28) 售价(29) 月销量(30) 利润率(31) 行动建议(32) twelve(33) little(34) stars(35) in(36) a(37) constellation(38) I(39) am(40) learning(41) to(42) read(43) by(44) heart(45)\n\nAbout 45 words.\n\n\"I called across the water to a market called Sorftime, and the water answered with a long string of numbers, a kind of incantation, and gave me back a hundred small plastic dreams made in someone else's workshop.\